* NOW, DO YOU LOVE ME *

22:42.328 --> 22:43.329
* DO YOU LOVE ME *

22:43.396 --> 22:45.197
* DO YOU LOVE ME *

22:45.264 --> 22:46.566
* DO YOU LOVE ME *

22:46.633 --> 22:51.170
* NOW THAT I CAN DANCE? *

22:51.237 --> 22:52.872
* DANCE *

